Name: Jumping Pirates
About the game: Jumping Pirates are fun adventures where you have to get to the finish line alive but there are some problems with that ... Overcome obstacles, collect coins, avoid water and sharp objects! A real cubic platformer where you will find everything - complex levels, nice voxel 3D graphics, summer and pirate atmosphere! Complete all levels and defeat all enemies! Many challenging levels full of dangerous traps and monsters Nice 3D graphics Gamepad support
